<h1>Welcome to Ooty</h1>
<p>
Ooty, also known as the Queen of Hills, is one of the most beautiful tourist places in Tamil Nadu.
It is famous for its cool climate, tea gardens, and scenic views.
</p>

<h2>Why Visit Ooty?</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Pleasant Climate</li>
    <li>Beautiful Hills</li>
    <li>Tea Plantations</li>
    <li>Peaceful Environment</li>
</ul>

